title: Ena antartiko sinialo CCF
description:
Ena xroniko ths drashs ths epanastatikhs organwshs Sunwmosia twn Purhnwn ths Fwtias, etsi opws katagrafetai mesa apo to logo ths alla kai opws to parousiasan ta mesa mazikhs enhmerwshs. 
To video "ENA ANTARTIKO SINIALO" egine prwth provolh th prwth mera tou dihmerou (15-16 Aprilh 2011) sto Polutexneio ths Thessalonikhs pou pragmatopoihse h "Suneleush Anarxikwn gia thn anatreptikh drash".
Oloklhrw8hke sth morfh pou einai twra kapoious mhnes meta kai egine provolh sto Anarxiko steki Nadir stis 8 Dekembrh 2011
